Jung Hyunwoo is just an unlucky gamer barely making ends meet in the VR game "God Wars." He even ends up losing access to his game account due to a horrible accident and is forced to create a new character. In the process, he discovers that he has an ability that allows him to see hidden information in the game, which leads him to become a Grand Warlock. Now equipped with a mind-blowing skill and a legendary class, all that's left is for him to level up and go from zero to hero...
(Source: Tapas)

Lee Hojae had given up his life as a pro gamer, until one day he received a mysterious message: Congratulations! Youve been invited to the Tutorial World. Intrigued, he enters the game and confidently chooses hell difficulty, but soon learns that he is trapped there. With a mere 0.01% survival rate, Hojae must somehow overcome the games agonizing challenges to figure out the real reason he was invited. This tutorial may be tough, but its secrets are whats truly hellacious. (Source: Tapas)
